  "detailed_description": "A Time Paradox is a puzzle game where you look for a way out that does not create a paradox. Each move matters, the goal is to reach each level exit without being seen by someone from the past (mostly yourself !). Be aware not to block a future your-self ! Anticipation and planning are key skills that will help you go through all the levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167730/extras/d96f5ca5d1279e6e8d49a8f1e166ba14.poster.avif?t=1598972700\" width=320 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167730/extras/d96f5ca5d1279e6e8d49a8f1e166ba14.webm?t=1598972700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167730/extras/d96f5ca5d1279e6e8d49a8f1e166ba14.mp4?t=1598972700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game have a single player story mode of about 80 levels, a 2 players cooperative mode, and multiple multiplayer mini games to share good time with friends !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167730/extras/b3a05039f2ca72874be3ceea06c53c7e.avif?t=1598972700\" width=540 height=381 /></span><br><br>A Time Paradox already hooked hundreds of players on Android, but only the PC version will give you high level of comfort for multiplayer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167730/extras/9361877438327f37dad21c4298eb9182.avif?t=1598972700\" width=540 height=592 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "A Time Paradox is a puzzle game where you look for a way out that does not create a paradox. Each move matters, the goal is to reach each level exit without being seen by someone from the past (mostly yourself !). Be aware not to block a future your-self ! Anticipation and planning are key skills that will help you go through all the levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167730/extras/d96f5ca5d1279e6e8d49a8f1e166ba14.poster.avif?t=1598972700\" width=320 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167730/extras/d96f5ca5d1279e6e8d49a8f1e166ba14.webm?t=1598972700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167730/extras/d96f5ca5d1279e6e8d49a8f1e166ba14.mp4?t=1598972700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game have a single player story mode of about 80 levels, a 2 players cooperative mode, and multiple multiplayer mini games to share good time with friends !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167730/extras/b3a05039f2ca72874be3ceea06c53c7e.avif?t=1598972700\" width=540 height=381 /></span><br><br>A Time Paradox already hooked hundreds of players on Android, but only the PC version will give you high level of comfort for multiplayer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167730/extras/9361877438327f37dad21c4298eb9182.avif?t=1598972700\" width=540 height=592 /></span>",
